<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Queensland flood relief billet volunteering</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag :all %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag :defaults %>
  <%= formtastic_stylesheet_link_tag %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tag %>
</head>
<body>
  
<div id="page">
  
<div id="header">
<img src ="/images/getup-logo-on-black.gif" alt="GetUp! Action for Australia">
</div><!-- // #header -->

<div id="content">
  
<div class="blurb">
<img class="photo" src="/images/flood-photo.gif" alt="Brisbane houses under water">
<p>
Australia is experiencing massive floods that have put an area larger than Texas underwater. In the next 2 hours much of the city of Brisbane will be flooded - about 30,000 to 50,000 homes will be lost.
</p>
<p><em>
Do you have space to take in someone displaced by the flood?
</em></p>
<h2>Volunteer now to help:</h2>
</div><!-- // .blurb -->

<div id ="app" class="box-shadow">

<%= yield %>

</div><!-- // #app -->

</div><!-- // #content -->

</div><!-- // #page -->
</body>
</html>